-==// Copilot //==-

A restful API built to fill the role of a middle tier data access layer for TS Software and Services.

To Do:
	- Encapsulate the classes which are considered to be part of the app core.
	- Write the automatic json->path creator.
	- Extend Data class to handle queueing and output return.
	- Further extend Data class by structuring output return to contain necessary overhead.
	- Output json responses to "output" textbox while DEV = true.


