Namespace & Class Structure

	Namespace - \

	Namespace - \CP
			Class - Copilot
			Class - Log
			Class - Data
			Class - DB

	Namespace - \CP\API
			Class - Rest
			Class - Paths
			Class - Adapter
			
	Namespace - \APP\PILOT
			Class - DB
			Class - tss_main



Sublime project files are setup to access C:\Program Files (x86)\Zend\Apache2\htdocs\copilot.

